<item>
            <title>[LU-15647] &quot;lfs df&quot; should not loop indefinitely for new MDTs/OSTs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15647</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The inner loop in &lt;tt&gt;lfs_df-&amp;gt;mntdf()&lt;/tt&gt; iterating over MDTs and OSTs will run forever if &lt;tt&gt;ENODEV&lt;/tt&gt; is not returned, even if other errors are returned:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; (tp = types; tp-&amp;gt;st_name != NULL; tp++) {
                bool have_ost = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;;

                &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (!(tp-&amp;gt;st_op &amp;amp; ops))
                        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;continue&lt;/span&gt;;

                &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; (index = 0; ; index++) {
                       rc2 = llapi_obd_fstatfs(fd, type, index, &amp;amp;stat_buf, &amp;amp;uuid_buf);
                        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (rc2 == -ENODEV)
                                &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;break&lt;/span&gt;;
                        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (rc2 == -EAGAIN)
                                &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;continue&lt;/span&gt;;
                        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (rc2 == -ENODATA) { &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;/* Inactive device, OK. */&lt;/span&gt;
                                &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (!(flags &amp;amp; MNTDF_VERBOSE))
                                        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;continue&lt;/span&gt;;
                        } &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (rc2 &amp;lt; 0 &amp;amp;&amp;amp; rc == 0) {
                                rc = rc2;
                        }
                        :
                }
        }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The inner loop should be limited to a maximum index of &lt;tt&gt;LOV_ALL_STRIPES&lt;/tt&gt; (to avoid looping forever) and a maximum of &lt;tt&gt;LL_STATFS_MAX&lt;/tt&gt; actual targets (to avoid overflowing the &lt;tt&gt;lsb-&amp;gt;sb_buf[]&lt;/tt&gt; array). &lt;/p&gt;</description>
